## Summary
This documentation page provides step-by-step instructions for setting up Single Sign-On (SSO) integration between Amplitude and Microsoft Azure Active Directory, including configuring the Enterprise application in Azure portal, setting identifier values, and uploading the metadata XML file to Amplitude's SSO settings.

